t:
Just another hour and I'll reach    
home, I was excited.                      


I watched in horror as                    
the time changed from                  
9:59 AM to 9:00 AM,                   
again.
c:
The journey is endless, I'll go for eternity. I am trapped in space-time.



#time #journey #trapped #loop #helpless #scifi #excitement #backintime
